OL,3,CParent says plans to repair bridges
OL,4,Cwill add '250 miles per week' to
OL,5,Cschool run
OL,7,FA parent from Cumbria says the four-
OL,8,Fyear plan to repair bridges on the M6
OL,9,Fwill add "an extra 250 miles per week"
OL,10,Fto her school run.
OL,12,FNational Highways announced plans to
OL,13,Freplace eight bridges from junctions
OL,14,F37 to 39, through Lune Gorge, last
OL,15,Fyear. The works, starting from 2027
OL,16,Fand finishing in 2031, are expected to
OL,17,Fmake the bridges safe for the next
OL,18,Fcentury.
