OL,3,CParent says plans to repair bridges
OL,4,Cwill add '250 miles per week' to
OL,5,Cschool run
OL,7,FThe works would result in the partial
OL,8,Fclosure of junction 38 at Tebay,
OL,9,Fallowing movement in one direction.
OL,11,FThe design of the scheme is yet to be
OL,12,Ffinalised. National Highways say they
OL,13,Fhave held several public information
OL,14,Fevents for residents.
OL,16,FLocal campaigner Charlotte Innif said:
OL,17,F"I'll have to drive 250 extra miles
OL,18,Fper week to get my children to and
OL,19,Ffrom school.
