OL,3,CParent says plans to repair bridges
OL,4,Cwill add '250 miles per week' to
OL,5,Cschool run
OL,7,F"It's going to cost me roughly #3000
OL,8,Fin fuel and time - and that's just me.
OL,9,FIt's going to affect tens, hundreds,
OL,10,Fif not thousands of people who use J38
OL,11,Fand the A6A5."
OL,13,FA campaign called the 'Keep Junction
OL,14,F38 Open' has been launched by
OL,15,Factivists.
OL,17,FMore than 1,700 people from
OL,18,Fcommunities across Orton, Tebay and
OL,19,FKirkby Stephen have expressed concerns
OL,20,Fthat the partial closure of junction
OL,21,F38 will have a major impact.
