OL,4,Cwill add '250 miles per week' to
OL,5,Cschool run
OL,7,FB&B owner Joanna Nugent thinks she'll
OL,8,Flose around 40 per cent of her income.
OL,9,FShe added: "I estimate that 80 per
OL,10,Fcent of our business comes from our
OL,11,Flocation, people travelling up and
OL,12,Fdown the motorway.
OL,14,F"An awful lot of our business is one-
OL,15,Fnight stays, people travelling from
OL,16,FLondon to Scotland on holiday, or
OL,17,Fvisiting family, etc.
