OL,3,CParent says plans to repair bridges
OL,4,Cwill add '250 miles per week' to
OL,5,Cschool run
OL,7,F"If you close half of the motorway,
OL,8,Fthat's 40 per cent of our business
OL,9,Fjust disappeared overnight. If
OL,10,Fsomebody just wipes off nearly half of
OL,11,Fyour income overnight, until that
OL,12,Fhappens, you don't really know what
OL,13,Fyou're going to be able to do."
OL,15,FA National Highways spokesperson said:
OL,16,F"This work is vital to keep drivers
OL,17,Fsafe and maintain the structures for
OL,18,Fthe future, and we continue to work
OL,19,Fwith local communities and businesses
OL,20,Fnearby to limit the impact.
