OL,7,F"When the main work begins in 2027,
OL,8,Four aim is to cause as little
OL,9,Fdisruption as possible, and junction
OL,10,F38 will be accessible for the duration
OL,11,Fof the project apart from the
OL,12,Foccasional overnight or weekend
OL,13,Fclosure, which will be kept to a
OL,14,Fminimum."
